<header class="music-heading">
  <div class="intro-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 mx-auto transparent-dark-container">
          <h2>My Music</h2>
          <p class="intro-text">
            Music has always been a large part of my life. Much like programming, music is a craft that you endlessly practise, improve and refine. There is always something new to master and
            it is always fun. From an early age, I found practising the piano was a way to unwind and escape for a while.
          </p>
          <p class="intro-text">
            Scroll down for a peek at some of my music projects to date.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#my" class="arrow js-scroll-trigger">
        <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-down animated fa-4x"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 text-center">
        <h2 id="my">My Projects</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <% case Date.today.strftime("%A").upcase %>
        <% when 'MONDAY' || 'TUESDAY' %>
          <%= render 'synthesia_video_1' %>
        <% when 'WEDNESDAY' || 'THURSDAY' %>
          <%= render 'synthesia_video_1' %>
        <% when 'FRIDAY' || 'SATURDAY' %>
          <%= render 'synthesia_video_1' %>
        <% when 'SUNDAY' %>
        <% else %>
          <%= render 'synthesia_video_3' %>
        <% end %>
        <p class="text-center">
          Using <%= link_to 'Ableton', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ableton_Live', target: '_blank' %>
          , <%= link_to 'OBS', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_Broadcaster_Software', target: '_blank' %>
          , <%= link_to 'Synthesia', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Synthesia', target: '_blank' %>
          and <%= link_to 'GIMP', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GIMP', target: '_blank' %> I recorded my performance
          and put together a visual tutorial as to how it is played so the viewer can learn to play it for themselves.
          Have a little watch yourself.
        </p>

        <p class="text-center">
          This video belongs to a separate YouTube channel of mine which is solely for Synthesia tutorials like
          this. <%= link_to 'Visit my Synthesia YouTube Channel', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gv-4Mk9xV7E&list=UUJCLykUyNiUHtK-2T6wjkow&index=1', target: '_blank' %>
          for more.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <% case Date.today.strftime("%A").upcase %>
        <% when 'MONDAY' || 'TUESDAY' %>
          <%= render 'youtube_video_1' %>
        <% when 'WEDNESDAY' || 'THURSDAY' %>
          <%= render 'youtube_video_2' %>
        <% when 'FRIDAY' || 'SATURDAY' %>
          <%= render 'youtube_video_3' %>
        <% when 'SUNDAY' %>
        <% else %>
          <%= render 'youtube_video_3' %>
        <% end %>
        <p class="text-center">
          This video belongs to a separate YouTube channel of mine which is solely for piano solo
          videos. <%= link_to 'Visit my Piano Solo YouTube Channel', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_pFmyxkRgWE&list=UUAiArHrQ_ypBh5ygHZWkyUA&index=2', target: '_blank' %>
          for more.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
        <% case Date.today.strftime("%A").upcase %>
        <% when 'MONDAY' || 'TUESDAY' %>
          <%= render 'soundcloud_video_1' %>
        <% when 'WEDNESDAY' || 'THURSDAY' %>
          <%= render 'soundcloud_video_2' %>
        <% when 'FRIDAY' || 'SATURDAY' %>
          <%= render 'soundcloud_video_3' %>
        <% when 'SUNDAY' %>
        <% else %>
          <%= render 'soundcloud_video_3' %>
        <% end %>
        <p class="text-center">
          You can <%= link_to 'visit my Soundcloud page', 'https://soundcloud.com/yamadaj2', target: '_blank' %> to
          listen to more of my piano solo tracks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="text-center">
  <%= link_to 'Back', root_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg" %>
</div>